}{}$$ \mathrm{RIB}={\sum}_{i\epsilon m}^m\frac{L_i}{L\max_i}, $$\end{document}where Li is the pathogen relative load (40-Ct) for that sample, Lmaxi is the highest relative load of that agent observed in the sample population and m is the sum of Li/Lmaxi for all pathogens detected in the sample.
